NOTE ON BUNDLED / DOWNLOADED MODELS:

ai-chan does NOT distribute LLM weights. Users download base models
themselves (e.g., Sarashina2-7B under MIT license from SB Intuitions).
Each downloaded model is governed by its own license — see
docs/MODEL_BASELINE.md and docs/LICENSES.md for details.

THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES:

Python dependencies are listed in requirements.txt / requirements.lock.
License compliance is auto-audited by scripts/check_licenses.py;
results are published in docs/LICENSES.md.
